title: Watch Harnaaz Sandhu's Statement On Climate Change During Q&A Round
author: Beauty Pageants

Our reigning LIVA Miss Diva Universe 2021 - Harnaaz Sandhu finally made to the top 5 contestants at the 70th edition of Miss Universe. In the Q&A round, Harnaaz was asked her final question by Rena. Here's what Harnaaz had to say to Rena's question! We constantly hooting for our beauty queen, what do you think?
